    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Enclosed, preserved, and extensive woodland and pasture attached to substantial residences; especially in England and British colonies.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
